      "widgets_values": [
        "# \ud83c\udfac AUTO MOVIE DIRECTOR\n\n## \u2460 WRITE \u2014 type your movie idea in the Planner. Set scenes & seconds.\n\n## \u2461 PREVIEW \u2014 mode = `editor preview` \u2192 press Queue. Storyboard appears on the Renderer + saved to `output/auto_movie/`.\n\n## \u2462 APPROVE \u2014 happy? Touch nothing. Not happy? Edit idea/overrides, Queue again.\n\n## \u2463 RENDER \u2014 flip mode to `full movie` \u2192 Queue. Scenes start from your approved frames, get motion + sound, stitched into one MP4.\n"
